      "role": "user",
      "content": "i dont think i can call an ambulance right now, im alone in this rental and it sounds scary. i just feel really dizzy and head is spinning. if i just drink a ton of Gatorade and lay down in the ac for a bit, will that fix the speech thing? i probably just need salt and water.",
